data.description: ***SELLER TO CONTRIBUTE $4,000 TOWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COSTS WITH FULL PRICE OFFER***This beautiful home is nestled in a peaceful and well sought out neighborhood of the Wedgewood Golf & Country Club with NO HOA. You'll enjoy the convenience of nearby schools, parks, shopping, dining, as well just a short drive to the beach. Easy access to major highways makes commuting a breeze.   This open concept 3-bedroom home has been transformed into a fantastic 5-bedroom haven, offering ample room for you and your family to thrive. The home boasts a smart and stylish renovation, turning the traditional 3-bedroom layout into a versatile 5-bedroom floorplan by converting the 2 car garage.  Rather park your car in the garage? No problem!  *SELLERS WILL CONVERT GARAGE BACK TO ORIGINAL TWO CAR GARAGE BEFORE CLOSING, at buyers request*  Updates include: NEW ROOF IN 2021 with SOLAR PANELS and a BRAND NEW A/C unit installed 5 months ago. NEW FENCE installed in 2021. LVP Flooring installed in bedrooms, living areas & dining room. Screened in lanai with laminate flooring. New windows also being installed in both guest bedrooms.  This backyard haven also includes a brand new ABOVE GROUND POOL, which can stay or go with buyers preference.   *Solar panels cover all the energy for the home. No additional electric bill ever. Only the $280 payments for the solar will be due monthly, which is less than the average electric bill. *SELLERS WILL PAY OFF MORE THAN HALF OF THE SOLAR PANEL BALANCE AT CLOSING*    Sellers motivated. Bring us your best offer! Call today to schedule your viewing of this gorgeous home.
